com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang

Class Tensor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.Tensor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Tensor
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A multi-dimensional array of data. Represented internally as a single double[] array. This class is central to data handling in MindsEye, and may have some odd-looking or suprising optimizations.
    See Also:
